Contributors Agreement

By contributing to the Tow Truck Server project ("Project"), you agree to the following terms:

(a) Confidentiality: You acknowledge that any information or materials shared within the Project, including but not limited to code, documentation, and discussions, may be confidential and proprietary to the Project. You agree to maintain the confidentiality of such information and materials and not to disclose or use them for any purpose outside the scope of the Project without prior written consent from Tristan Kuhn or other authorized representatives of the Project.

(b) Ownership of Contributions: You retain ownership of any intellectual property rights in the contributions you make to the Project. However, by contributing to the Project, you grant Tristan Kuhn and other contributors a perpetual, irrevocable, worldwide, non-exclusive, royalty-free, sublicensable license to use, reproduce, modify, distribute, and otherwise exploit your contributions for the purposes of the Project.

(c) Restrictions on Redistribution: You agree not to redistribute the Software or any derivative works thereof, whether modified or unmodified, without prior written consent from Tristan Kuhn. This includes but is not limited to uploading the Software or derivative works to public repositories, forums, or other platforms accessible to third parties.

(d) Indemnification: You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Tristan Kuhn and other contributors to the Project from and against any claims, liabilities, damages, losses, or expenses arising out of or in connection with your contributions to the Project.

(e) Governing Law: This Contributors Agreement shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of [Your State/Country], without regard to its conflict of laws principles.

(f) Entire Agreement: This Contributors Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between you and Tristan Kuhn concerning your contributions to the Project and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous communications and proposals, whether oral or written, between you and Tristan Kuhn with respect to your contributions.

(g) Amendments: Tristan Kuhn reserves the right to modify this Contributors Agreement at any time. Any modifications will be effective upon posting on the Project's website or otherwise notifying you.

If you have any questions about this Contributors Agreement, please contact Tristan Kuhn at [Your Contact Information].

BY CONTRIBUTING TO THE PROJECT, YOU ACKNOWLEDGE THAT YOU HAVE READ THIS CONTRIBUTORS AGREEMENT, UNDERSTAND IT, AND AGREE TO BE BOUND BY ITS TERMS AND CONDITIONS.